EmailTemplate.subject: We're having a Gala in Winnipeg this September!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Contact.FirstName},
On September 21st, we’ll be having our first annual #LoveLegacy Gala at the Canadian Museum for Human Rights in Winnipeg. At this incredible venue, we’ll enjoy an evening of art, food, entertainment, and friends—with all proceeds going towards our work in Haiti.
We've attached the save the date image to this email. Full event details will be released shortly. We’d love to see you there!
The Team at Live Different
